hite-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-family: Cambria,serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-bbbe1c9c-7fff-110f-4533-e0ecd0293847\">Willpower points (WP) - like Health points (HP), but for determination of willpower capacity. Knocked unconscious when reached 0.</strong></span></p></li></ul>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":200000,"name":"Attributes","type":"text","_id":"mK6omCqD8T3qDhrX","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-82a81f3d-7fff-bc3c-5135-9e777f07ebd6\">Physical and mental capabilities of a character.</strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Strength (STR)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">HIT chance of all melee weapons.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">DMG of all melee weapons.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Tenacity - negation of flat physical damage.</span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Dexterity (DEX)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">HIT chance of all range or light melee weapons.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">DMG of all range or light melee weapons.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Dodge - increase AC.</span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><br /><strong>Constitution (CON)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">HP pool: 0=10HP.<br />Can't be lower than 5.Â </span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Each 1 CON holds a cost of 5HP.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Metabolism - recovery after physical injuries.</span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Intelligence (INT)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Each point allows you to learn a Discipline or upgrade a known one.</span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><br /><strong>Willpower (WIL)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">WP pool: 0=10WP.<br />Can't be lower than 5.Â </span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Each 1 WIL holds a cost of 5WP.Â </span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Equilibrium - recovery after mental/psychic injuries.Â </span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Charisma (CHA)</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Cambria,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Every 2 points add 1 milestone point.</span></p></li></ul><hr /><p><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-f514e53e-7fff-394e-4293-807f449c274b\">Each character </strong><strong>starts with 0</strong> for each attribute, which is an average stat for the world. <br />Gain <strong>3 attribute points</strong> to spend on <strong>1st level</strong>.<br />Receive <strong>1 attribute point </strong>on the <strong>5th and 10th levels</strong>.<br />Players can choose to <strong>relocate 2</strong> of these points at <strong>level 1</strong>. <br />Can move it down from -3 (child) to up to +5 (great athlete/scientist).<br />Can also be increased by <strong>Expertise</strong>.</span></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":550000,"name":"Armor class & Tenacity","type":"text","_id":"xwXMjU3iKhUMDt76","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Armor class (AC)<strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-2899e5ba-7fff-9e57-9d81-e5e0afe5141b\"> - how much to roll to hit the player.</strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><em><strong>AC = 6 + DEX + Equipment</strong></em></span></p><hr /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\">Tenacity (TN)<strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-2899e5ba-7fff-9e57-9d81-e5e0afe5141b\"> - how much flat physical damage can be soaked by a player.</strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><em><strong>TN = STR + Equipment</strong></em></span></p><p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":150000,"name":"Age","type":"text","_id":"bwtJZjENoOLnexoj","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-455290c6-7fff-0c83-205e-42205abaec74\">Each age bracket holds its advantages and disadvantages.</strong></span></p><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\"><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1pt;border-right:solid #000000 1pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1pt;border-top:solid #000000 1pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Age</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1pt;border-right:solid #000000 1pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1pt;border-top:solid #000000 1pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><strong>Attributes correlations</strong></span></p></td>